Title: Comments on ``Are Swift Gamma-Ray Bursts consistent with the Ghirlanda
  relation?", by Campana et al.(astro--ph/0703676)
Authors: G. Ghirlanda (1), L. Nava (1,2), G. Ghisellini (1), C. Firmani (1,3)
  ((1) Osserv. Astr. di Brera, (2) Univ. degli Studi dell'Insubria, (3)
  U.N.A.M.)
Categories: astro-ph
Comments: 3 pages
\\
  In their recent paper, Campana et al. (2007) found that 5 bursts, among those
detected by Swift, are outliers with respect to the E_peak-E_gamma
("Ghirlanda") correlation. We instead argue that they are not.
